On this day in 2017 all I had was faith, a computer & a few artist emails. I turnt ma dukes pantry into my studio. I never made excuses I always executed in some way. Doors was closed, ppl gave up, but I never stopped. I cried many times, didn’t know where to turn but I knew it’ll get greater later so I kept goin’ ‼️ On this same day in 2023… I’m a RIAA certified Multi Platinum producer, I’ve sold Millions of records, apart of tv shows, movies, & commercials. I’m Grammy nominated, all from not giving up. It’s never how you start it’s always how you finish & even though I reached some of the biggest milestones I’m no where near finished. Keep goin’ wherever you are in your life ‼️God is Tha Greatest 🙏🏽 🗣️ It’s Budda Beats 💨 Tha Biggest ‼️ #keepgoing
